text: BEAUTIFUL well maintained home in west Salem. Vaulted large open elegant living area, cooks dream kitchen, 3 large roomy bedrooms, 2 baths with tubs, 2 walk in closets, an awesome built in home stereo system. Large back deck and hot tub for relaxing after a long day. Low maintenance fenced yard, brand new Tough Shed, newer roof about 3-4 years old, large 2 car garage. Beautiful, peaceful neighborhood, close to shopping and restaurants. Enjoy the wineries in the area, short drive to McMinville.
nearby_schools: Oregon Department Of Education, Salem-Keizer School District 24j

text: Beautiful 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bath, with large kitchen, family room, an office in a quiet, beautiful landscape neighborhood in West Salem. Walking distance to West Salem High School, Straub Middle School and Chapman Hill Elementary School. The property is almost 10, 000 sqft sit back to the natural Chandler Park. There is a storage under the house with power and lights over 800 sqft. RV/Boat pad on the side of the house. Call listing agent Gina .
nearby_schools: Oregon Department Of Education, Salem-Keizer School District 24j

text: This home has been lovingly updated and cared for over the 30 years the owners have been here. Cute front patio, tile floors in kitchen, dining and baths, engineered hardwood floors throughout the rest of the house, large covered patio (33 x 10), new roof (8/20), new gutters, new furnace, garbage disposal, new vinyl windows, kitchen updated approx. 5 years ago, new garage door and opener, and 10x10 barn style shed. This is a great value for this home, come check it out before it's gone!
